Name: Average resolution time of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Median duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Shortest time to resolve a case after 'Unmatched + Unmatched' has occurred
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration between 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of all 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities within the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Closed' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time from first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' occurrence to last 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Accepted + Wait - User' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Unmatched + Unmatched' versus cases involving 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of a case with 'Unmatched + Unmatched' as the final activity before closure
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Maximum time gap between two consecutive 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in a single case
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Average duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the next occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in a different case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Cancelled' in cases where 'Completed + Cancelled' follows 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Duration from the first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' occurrence to the initiation of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Comparison of average duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + In Call' with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
